==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Transhumanize
<hw>Trans*hu"man*ize</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To make
more than human; to purity; to elevate above humanity.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Souls purified by sorrow and self-denial,
<qex>transhumanized</qex> to the divine abstraction of pure
contemplation.</q> <rj><qau>Lowell.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Transiency</ent>⟦br⟧
<ent>Transience</ent>⟦br⟧
